DOC.brief_summary: The purpose study ass ocular response performance cosmetically print silicone hydrogel contact lens AIR OPTIX® COLORS compare FRESHLOOK® COLORBLENDS .
DOC.detailed_description: The study conduct two phase . Phase 1 adaptation phase participant wear AIR OPTIX® AQUA contact lenses bilaterally ( product eye ) daily wear basis 1 week . In Phase 2 , participant wear AIR OPTIX® COLORS FRESHLOOK® COLORBLENDS contact lenses contralaterally ( different product eye ) daily wear basis 4 week .
DOC.criteria: Full legal capacity volunteer ; Read sign information consent letter ; Willing able follow instruction maintain appointment schedule ; Ocular examination last two year ; Currently wear soft contact lenses daily wear basis ; Contact lens prescription 1.50 diopter 5.00 diopter ; Other protocoldefined inclusion criterion may apply . Any ocular disease ; Any systemic condition may affect study outcome variable ; Any systemic topical medication may affect ocular health ; Known sensitivity diagnostic pharmaceutical use study ; Unable achieve acceptable fit study lenses ; Anisometropia > 1.00 diopter astigmatism > 0.75 diopter ; Use lubricating/rewetting eye drop . Other protocoldefined exclusion criterion may apply .
